---
import CTA from '../../../../components/CTA.astro';
import FeatureDetailPage from '../../../../components/FeatureDetailPage.astro';
import FeatureCard from '../../../../components/FeatureCard.astro';
---

<FeatureDetailPage
  title="Running Pace Calculator"
  description="Calculate your running pace, speed, and finish time for any distance."
  lang="en"
  currentPath="/pacelab/en/pace-calculator/"
  backHref="/pacelab/en/"
  backLabel="← Back to Pace Lab home"
>
  <p>Calculate your running pace, speed, and finish time for any distance.</p>
  <p>This running pace calculator helps you quickly convert between pace, time, and distance so you can plan your training and races more effectively.</p>

  <h2>What you can do</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Calculate pace from distance and time</li>
    <li>Convert pace to speed (km/h or mph)</li>
    <li>Estimate finish time for a target pace</li>
    <li>Adjust inputs instantly and see results</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>When to use it</h2>
  <p>Use this tool when you want to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Plan your marathon or half marathon pace</li>
    <li>Check your pace after a run</li>
    <li>Set a target pace for workouts</li>
    <li>Convert treadmill speed and outdoor pace</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Example</h2>
  <p>If you run 10 km in 50 minutes:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Pace: 5:00 min/km</li>
    <li>Speed: 12.0 km/h</li>
  </ul>
  <p>You can use this calculator to quickly test different pacing strategies.</p>

  <CTA
    title="Get the app"
    description="Use the full Pace Lab app for more features like split charts, race prediction, heart rate zones, and fueling planning."
    links={[
      { href: 'https://apps.apple.com/us/app/pace-lab-running-calculator/id6759136568', label: 'App Store' },
      { href: 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kr.slowlane.pacelab', label: 'Google Play' },
    ]}
  />

  <section class="section-block">
    <h2>Related tools</h2>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <FeatureCard href="/pacelab/en/race-pace-calculator/" title="Race pace calculator" description="Calculate the target pace for your goal time and distance, then view detailed race splits." />
      <FeatureCard href="/pacelab/en/400m-lap-calculator/" title="400m lap calculator" description="Convert pace to 400m lap time, or lap time to pace, for track workouts." />
      <FeatureCard href="/pacelab/en/training-pace-calculator/" title="Training pace calculator" description="Get recommended training paces for easy runs, marathon pace, threshold, and intervals." />
      <FeatureCard href="/pacelab/en/heart-rate-zone-calculator/" title="Heart rate zone calculator" description="Calculate heart rate zones using age, max HR, resting HR, or lactate threshold HR." />
      <FeatureCard href="/pacelab/en/race-time-predictor/" title="Race time predictor" description="Predict race times from a recent result with record-based and VDOT-based estimates." />
      <FeatureCard href="/pacelab/en/energy-gel-calculator/" title="Energy gel calculator" description="Plan gel count and intake timing based on your race distance, pace, and goal time." />
    </div>
  </section>
</FeatureDetailPage>
